5860793.effect:
You can Special Summon this card (from your hand) by banishing 1 "Explosive Powder Keg" from your field or GY. You can only control 1 "Captain Gangplank". Cannot be destroyed by card effects. Once per Chain (Quick Effect): You can target 1 "Explosive Powder Keg" on the field; destroy it. If this card is Special Summoned, or once per turn during the End Phase: You can activate 1 of these effects (but you can only use the 1st of these effects of "Captain Gangplank" once per turn);
●Add to your hand or Set 1 Spell/Trap from your Deck that mentions "Explosive Powder Keg".
●Special Summon 1 "Explosive Powder Keg" from your Deck, GY, or banishment.

5860824.effect:
